comments: Crowder (MEM) makes incidental contact to Covington's (MIN) arm after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Covington (MIN) makes slight contact with Brooks' (MEM) body while fighting through the screen.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) slightly extends his leg as part of an unnatural shooting motion on the jump shot attempt, but the contact with Dieng (MIN) is marginal.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) makes contact to Teague's (MIN) body during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Brooks (MEM) delivers contact to Covington's (MIN) head on the driving shot attempt.
Dieng (MIN) makes contact to Morant's (MEM) leg at the start of his drive, but does not affect his SQBR.
Morant (MEM) releases from Culver (MIN) at the start of his drive and does not affect his ability to defend.
Morant (MEM) makes contact to Teague's (MIN) body at the end of the drive but the contact is marginal.
Melton (MEM) jumps vertical prior to the contact to Teague (MIN). As Melton lands, he makes incidental contact to Teague's body, but does not dislodge him.
Dieng (MIN) makes contact to Melton's (MEM) arm that affects his control of the ball.
Crowder (MEM) makes contact to Wiggins' (MIN) body after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Teague (MIN) commits a take foul on Crowder (MEM).
